      "seed": 138548778,
      "version": 1983,
      "versionNonce": 1942973482,
      "isDeleted": false,
      "boundElements": [],
      "updated": 1782900047543,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "text": "The memory system is used for context building.\ncategories\n- short-term\n  - task\n  - previous result\n  - xxx\n- long-term\n  - soul\n  - user preference\n  - facts\n  - esopic\n  - procedure (rules)\n\nimplemenation:\n- files\n- physical memory\n- graphdb\n- vectordb\n- sql\n- fulltext search engine",
      "fontSize": 36,
      "fontFamily": 5,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "middle",
      "containerId": "xm6FIJvx4Z_03ToBFKJkw",
      "originalText": "The memory system is used for context building.\ncategories\n- short-term\n  - task\n  - previous result\n  - xxx\n- long-term\n  - soul\n  - user preference\n  - facts\n  - esopic\n  - procedure (rules)\n\nimplemenation:\n- files\n- physical memory\n- graphdb\n- vectordb\n- sql\n- fulltext search engine",
      "autoResize": true,
      "lineHeight": 1.25
    },
